Name: Bones
Title: The Twisted Bones in the Melted Truck
Desc: A human carcass is found melted to the dashboard of a charred truck.
LongDescription: Brennan and Booth investigate a crime scene where a human carcass has melted to the dashboard of a charred truck; Sweets tries to keep his feelings for Daisy from interfering while helping her pass a government psychological evaluation.
